nodes.text: The Dark Vortex Club was a seedy nightclub on Coruscant, that was also the site of a lot of criminal activity. It was owned by the Ubese Mah-Luu and entry into it could only be gained through a Darth Vader figurine. Senator Luralon Odaay was a regular patron at it and he liked to engage in the services of the prostitute Kandi there. Following his death, two New Republic agents visited the club as part of their investigations.
